    "innerText": "Enable Auto-Update?\n\nMerlio will estimate monthly CPF contributions based on your salary and age, and add them to your balances each month automatically. Figures are for planning reference only — refer to the CPF website for actual balances.\n\nI have verified my CPF balances against the CPF website and they are up to date.\nNot yet\nGot it, enable",
    "outerHTML": "<div class=\"w-full max-w-sm rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-5\" style=\"background: rgb(42, 37, 32); border: 1px solid rgba(212, 160, 82, 0.2);\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-serif text-[#c4bdb4]\">Enable Auto-Update?</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-[#7a7068] font-sans leading-relaxed\">Merlio will estimate monthly CPF contributions based on your salary and age, and add them to your balances each month automatically. Figures are for planning reference only — refer to the CPF website for actual balances.</p></div><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group\"><div class=\"relative mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"sr-only\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\" style=\"background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\"></div></div><span class=\"text-xs font-sans leading-relaxed text-[#a09890] group-hover:text-[#c4bdb4] transition-colors\">I have verified my CPF balances against the CPF website and they are up to date.</span></label><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex-1 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-sans text-[#7a7068] transition-colors hover:text-[#c4bdb4]\" style=\"background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\">Not yet</button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"flex-1 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-sans font-medium transition-all disabled:opacity-30\" style=\"background: rgba(212, 160, 82, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(212, 160, 82, 0.3); color: rgb(212, 160, 82);\">Got it, enable</button></div></div>",
